==Trivia==
*They appear to use all attack styles when using [[melee]], depending on the animation they use: [[slashing]] when they use their talons, [[stabbing]] when they jab with their tail and [[crushing]] when they bite the target.
*Ancient wyverns had a festive override wearing a [[yellow partyhat]] during the [[2017 Christmas event/Gallery|2017]], [[2018 Christmas event/Gallery|2018]], and [[2019 Christmas event/Gallery|2019]] Christmas events.

